title: Office of the President
description:
Jim Harbaugh wants answers for sexual abuse victim Jon Vaughn but the President won't even take the time to speak with him (00:40:00). Gerry Callahan power ranks fentanyl deaths in the wake of Bob Saget's death (00:01:45). Kirkin' Off compares Kirk to Antonio Brown and mocks his mental health (00:24:20). Chris may have admitted defeat... He has brought in the Warthog to save 'At A Theater Near Me' (00:53:38). Rico Bosco & Big Cat join, a Jared Carrabis update & more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
